WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:01.973
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.973 --> 00:00:03.063
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.063 --> 00:00:05.080
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:08.600
Well, it's Diana, my sweetheart, and we're excited to be here.

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:11.530
We have some things the Holy Spirit has told us to talk about.

00:00:11.530 --> 00:00:18.400
Yesterday in the livestream, the Lord was warning us about a Monica Lewinsky-type of a scandal.

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.823
And a lot of people were really freaked out about that.

00:00:20.823 --> 00:00:22.333
But I've already warned you.

00:00:22.333 --> 00:00:30.040
I kept seeing, remember the cobblestone path, and I saw the blonde lady with a really nice dress on.

00:00:30.040 --> 00:00:35.349
She was a beautiful blonde lady, and nobody saw her coming.

00:00:35.349 --> 00:00:41.880
This warning that the cobblestone path the Lord has told me about was about Donald Trump, and to intercede and pray for him.

00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:44.960
He showed me him walking down a cobblestone path.

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:52.189
I don't know if this is legitimately a cobblestone path or if this is something that's like a type and shadow of something.

00:00:52.189 --> 00:01:05.360
And this woman that is absolutely beautiful—this woman had blonde hair, she had a French twist in the back of her hair, and she was dressed up in this beautiful dress, and she was there to take him out.

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:11.609
The Secret Service, the people that were around, were not guarded up because of this woman's beauty.

00:01:11.609 --> 00:01:17.874
So I don't know if this is, like I said, a type and shadow of somebody that is trying to seduce him or whatever.

00:01:17.874 --> 00:01:18.869
I don't know.

00:01:18.869 --> 00:01:23.566
Nobody saw her coming, and even the Secret Service didn't see her coming.

00:01:23.566 --> 00:01:25.320
But the Lord spoke to me.

00:01:25.320 --> 00:01:29.560
He said, "Brennan, not everything that I show you is just point-blank.

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:33.480
It's not as it seems.

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:35.040
It can be like a type and shadow.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.320
" Yeah, that's what I want to say.

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:37.600
It's a type and shadow.

00:01:37.600 --> 00:01:42.880
And so, whenever he was telling me, he said, "I want you to pray into that.

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:46.960
" And now I'm seeing who the blonde-headed woman is.

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:59.492
And I want to say, whenever he's been talking to us about JFK—and it would be a type of JFK, yeah, he was assassinated and things happened—but the Lord said, "Marilyn Monroes, Monica Lewinsky's...

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.120
pray over his marriage.

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:10.906
" I don't know how many times the Lord has said, "pray over his marriage.

00:02:10.906 --> 00:02:12.879
" Arranged things like that...

00:02:12.879 --> 00:02:23.177
there are very strong words that I get when I'm praying in the Spirit over President Trump's marriage: "paid off," things like that.

00:02:23.177 --> 00:02:28.100
These are hard words, but they're the reality of what I feel we're praying over.

00:02:28.100 --> 00:02:40.018
And it's something to be serious about, folks, because he must finish his assignment for what the Lord has called him to do.

00:02:40.018 --> 00:02:47.010
And the only way he will do this, I really truly believe, ladies and gentlemen, is by this body of intercessors interceding for him.

00:02:47.010 --> 00:02:53.360
He was the log in the road concerning the Antichrist agenda.

00:02:53.360 --> 00:03:05.040
Everybody else was lined up ready, but we had Trump in the road as an oak tree log blocking the path of all this, trying to be the buffer.

00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:11.529
So, you automatically know that the enemy is not happy about that, and he wants to take him out of the way.

00:03:11.529 --> 00:03:23.080
So, I've already told you all that I saw the Iranian government saying, "If we can't get to him, we'll hurt his kids or his grandkids, or we have an assignment about this.

00:03:23.080 --> 00:03:25.165
" So, it's coming in every single direction.

00:03:25.165 --> 00:03:31.200
And even the Lord said about his heart, about his arteries, about all these things.

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:33.479
So, he is a threat obviously.

00:03:33.479 --> 00:03:35.336
So now here's another one.

00:03:35.336 --> 00:03:41.733
The Lord is warning us about—hopefully it's not already started—a Monica Lewinsky-type sex scandal.

00:03:45.920 --> 00:03:57.653
And I saw a beautiful blonde woman, a woman that was poised and very polished in the way she talks, trying to...

00:03:57.653 --> 00:04:03.040
and like I said, I'm not always going to just blame—it's probably going to blame the woman, say it's the woman's fault.

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:04.860
It takes two to tango, right?

00:04:04.860 --> 00:04:05.520
It takes two.

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:07.939
So, we're not going to go, "Well, it's her fault, it's his fault.

00:04:08.616 --> 00:04:09.760
" No, it's the devil's fault.

00:04:09.760 --> 00:04:12.497
And he works with hormones, and he works with all kinds of things.

00:04:12.497 --> 00:04:15.680
And if he can get an inch, he'll take a mile.

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:29.703
And so, that's part of this prayer assignment, is to pray a hedge of protection around him that he would be like a Joseph and flee these situations, saying, "Listen, I've got a job to do, and this isn't about this.

00:04:31.200 --> 00:04:33.979
I'm going to do what God has called me to do, obviously.

00:04:33.979 --> 00:04:44.926
" And we put prayer warriors assigned around and about him to make sure that he stays on target, because bottom line, ladies and gentlemen, it's about what God has for President Trump.

00:04:44.926 --> 00:04:46.126
You may not like him.

00:04:46.126 --> 00:04:48.126
I'm not in politics, folks.

00:04:48.126 --> 00:04:54.434
I'm not, "Well, it's red, it's blue, it's Republican, it's Democrat, it's the New Party, it's whatever.

00:04:54.434 --> 00:05:04.338
