00:05:04.338 --> 00:05:06.434
And God's not done with America yet.

00:05:06.434 --> 00:05:14.453
But it's about getting the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous with this end-time wealth transfer for the Body of Christ, from what I've seen.

00:05:14.453 --> 00:05:16.512
And there's a great assignment for this.

00:05:16.512 --> 00:05:17.520
And people go...

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:19.759
I want to say this, folks.

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:28.124
I'm not here to talk about money and tell you that you're going to be rich if you put your fifty-eight dollars in the bucket.

00:05:28.124 --> 00:05:36.811
I'm here to tell you, if you follow the voice of God for yourself, He'll bless you exceedingly, abundantly, above all that you dare ask or think.

00:05:36.811 --> 00:05:39.920
Because that's just the Word; He said He would do that.

00:05:39.920 --> 00:05:42.903
But I'm not into all the gimmicks of things.

00:05:42.903 --> 00:05:45.200
I'm just telling you, it's just black and white with me.

00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:48.800
It's just the Word, what He said He would do for us.

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:54.537
And I'm telling you, it's time for us to walk in the abundance to the extreme, to where it overflows.

00:05:54.537 --> 00:06:05.039
Not to be arrogant and inflated with pride, but to be a vessel that God can use to pour out His blessing upon people who need it.

00:06:05.039 --> 00:06:06.090
If you don't have it...

00:06:06.090 --> 00:06:09.110
it's like the youth building, for instance, in our church.

00:06:09.500 --> 00:06:13.360
There shouldn't be a need of them having to go, "Well, you know what?

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:17.740
We can't do the project because there's not enough money there to do it.

00:06:17.740 --> 00:06:25.260
" It should have a storehouse in the account for the Body of Christ to say, "Listen, we need new cameras, we need new paint, we need to do this stuff.

00:06:25.260 --> 00:06:31.154
" And we don't have to raise a fundraiser to put a parking lot in for the revival.

00:06:31.154 --> 00:06:37.720
Well, we've got this five acres, but there's no money, and we have to believe God, and God's like, "You know what?

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:45.519
It's time for the exceedingly, abundantly, above all that we dare ask or think, to be the people, the lenders that say, 'I've got it.

00:06:45.519 --> 00:06:47.553
Let's just write the check and get this thing done.

00:06:47.553 --> 00:06:48.617
Find the contractor.

00:06:48.617 --> 00:06:52.285
Let's do it and get it done as quickly as possible.

00:06:52.285 --> 00:06:55.280
In fact, we're behind schedule.

00:06:55.280 --> 00:07:01.280
' Not to go, 'Well, you know, if the money comes in, folks, until it does, we can't get the project done.

00:07:01.280 --> 00:07:03.680
' We're out of time.

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:04.280
Do you understand?

00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:06.319
The Lord keeps telling me, 'Brennan, we're out of time.

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:11.759
' We're behind schedule with where we are right now and the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:07:11.759 --> 00:07:20.160
Folks, we should already be as scouts, like I like being a watchman, seeing years in advance.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:22.251
I'm trying to warn you of what's coming.

00:07:22.251 --> 00:07:22.526
A plague's coming.

00:07:23.260 --> 00:07:25.559
War is on the shore.

00:07:25.559 --> 00:07:28.251
