00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:18.920
And I was trying to warn you what was said not even 48 hours after I gave, 24 hours, whatever it was, after I gave you the word from the Holy Ghost, telling you what the Holy Spirit tells you all prophetically.

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:20.350
