And it was serious.

00:09:26.124 --> 00:09:30.168
And that's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:36.286
This is something that, you know, people say, "Well, Brandon, with the visions that you see, can we stop this?

00:09:52.640 --> 00:09:57.320
" Even our pastor said, "Do you feel like we can delay this?

00:09:57.320 --> 00:10:01.984
" I said, "We always can pray into something and stop something.

