A blood moon coming.

00:10:36.373 --> 00:10:42.160
Seven billion people will be able to see this blood moon that's coming in September.

00:10:42.160 --> 00:10:52.319
I didn't even know there was an eclipse, but it's a seven billion potential to see this blood moon, a full blood moon over an area.

00:10:56.800 --> 00:10:57.333
And those are signs in the heavens.

00:10:57.333 --> 00:11:26.400
Signs in the heavens in September, the month you remember all these things that the Lord has already been talking to us about regarding September and warning us to pray over Rosh Hashanah and over this timeframe from September 23rd, with the UN making their choices and saying, "Hey, we want to divide Jerusalem and all these things, and a two-state solution, recognizing Palestine as a state and all these things.

